paragraph
 Languages <b>with</b> Runtime Guards include <a href="haskell.html">Haskell</a>, <a href="elixir.html">Elixir</a>

exampleCodeHeader Example from <a href="haskell.html">Haskell</a>:

code
 f x
  | x &gt; 0 = 1
  | otherwise = 0

exampleCodeHeader Example from <a href="elixir.html">Elixir</a>:

code
 def abs(number) when number &gt; 0, do: number
 def abs(number), do: -number



















